Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.task

Class MemberInTaskDto

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.task.MemberInTaskDto
public class MemberInTaskDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object for representing a member involved in a task. This class encapsulates details about the member, including their ID, name, role in the task, role in the project, system name, and a link to their photo.
